snippet.title: WATCH: Sentencing phase continues in trial of Amber Guyger following murder conviction
snippet.description:
The sentencing phase of the trial for a former Dallas police officer convicted of murdering her neighbor continues Wednesday. The state began presenting its case for punishment on Tuesday afternoon, after the jury found Amber Guyger guilty of murder. The jury delivered the verdict after about six hours of deliberating.
